## 🆓 Free & Premium

### Free

* **3 sessions** included
* Full game, no functional limitation
* Each session consumes **1 play**

### Premium

* **Unlimited play** (for this game only, on this device)
* Unlocks **Mistakes only** mode
  Replay only the items you previously got wrong
* Activation via local code
* No account, no server sync

All rules are implemented in `storage.js`.

---

## 💳 Payments, Data & Privacy

* No account
* No backend
* No tracking
* All data stored **locally** in the browser

Payments are processed by **Stripe Checkout**.
Payment data is handled by Stripe and never stored by the game.

Premium activation uses a local code (`WT-XXXX-XXXX`), stored only on the device.

